{"id": 2960, "genre": 1001, "title": "《权力的游戏》完结，都给你带来了哪些暴击感的遗憾？", "description": "曾一度被众多观众认为是史上最伟大的美剧，就这么潦草地画上了句点。", "record_count": 3935, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20190521101802A3ocF7TuvQVMOBna.jpeg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2019-05-21T03:00:54Z", "options": [{"id": 344832, "content": "铺垫了这么久的夜王之战和权利之战，就潦草结束了？话说夜王被编的太弱了吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1070751}, {"id": 344835, "content": "一切都很莫名其妙，只有二丫和三傻的结局是我觉得很圆满、适合他们的结局。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1381695}, {"id": 345860, "content": "你以为我跑大老远干什么来了？\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1657697}, {"id": 344837, "content": "布兰:我不姓史塔克，我对权力没有兴趣。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1580365}, {"id": 344843, "content": "竹篮打水一场空，前面根本没有铺垫布兰，snow才是王、snow才是王、snow才是王！删了重拍", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655229}, {"id": 344844, "content": "Jon这个最合法的王位继承人竟然没坐上铁王座，又被发配到边疆了😂", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 251362}, {"id": 344850, "content": "布兰的一句要不然我这一路过来是干嘛的，简直毁掉这个人物，搞了半天三眼乌鸦是谋划王位的吗？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1231084}, {"id": 344851, "content": "所有人都受到了来自编剧的降智打击", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1522913}, {"id": 344859, "content": "布兰那句你以为我走到现在是为了什么？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634906}, {"id": 344860, "content": "瘸腿一世", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1634906}, {"id": 344865, "content": "一切都是梦撒，醒来斯诺还是守夜人，屎塔克家族还是北境之王，各个领主也不过还了个人，最后的最后没人记得还有夜王这一回事，对了，每个人还可以自己给自己立传。真绝了，不是应该死后才立吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 838588}, {"id": 344611, "content": "选国王那段和选小学班长有啥区别", "image": null, "praise_count": 750, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688713}, {"id": 344875, "content": "U R MY QUEEN.... AND MUNDER", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1655371}, {"id": 344622, "content": "妇联4拍的真好", "image": null, "praise_count": 244, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1352161}, {"id": 344623, "content": "如果雪诺在杀了丹妮丽丝之后自杀会好一点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 310, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1577579}, {"id": 345391, "content": "神剧烂尾它做到了前无古人后无来者！追了7季的青春，我是喂了狗了！手动再见", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1656377}, {"id": 344624, "content": "这个凛冬，有点像海南的冬天，说走就走", "image": null, "praise_count": 180, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1654821}, {"id": 344625, "content": "编剧确实功力比马丁差多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 107, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1531519}, {"id": 344628, "content": "夜王怎么就没复活的大招呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 42, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1529240}, {"id": 344884, "content": "从夜王被偷袭的那一刻，整个剧就开始不对了，太诡异！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1445937}, {"id": 344629, "content": "权力才是整个剧的主角", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1648425}, {"id": 344630, "content": "布兰翻了几季白眼咋就成王了？", "image": "img/option/option/20190521113047cuMTWNbfQz8I46dR.jpg", "praise_count": 355, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1632726}, {"id": 344631, "content": "为什么腾讯视频还不可以看？", "image": null, "praise_count": 41, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1147277}, {"id": 344632, "content": "夜王南下的原因 和人类的关系没讲清楚 \nbran铺垫那么多季 最后除了告诉个真实身份 全程划水 最后还当了国王？？\njammie 和briane的友谊到爱情\n最后的强行民主", "image": null, "praise_count": 80, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1481654}, {"id": 344633, "content": "龙妈就这样死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 65, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1178586}, {"id": 344634, "content": "第八季要是能重拍就好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 109, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1162994}, {"id": 344891, "conten